{"id":316604,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-黑龙江访民王玉波钓鱼台撒传单被拘留（/","date":"2013-10-05T03:33:00Z","modified":"2013-10-05T03:33:00Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江访民王玉波钓鱼台撒传单被拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）黑龙江省佳木斯市上访维权者王玉波、初东芳、于丽华、吕双丽四人，因上访问题长期得不到解决，故于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日在北京钓鱼台国宾馆撒传单，表达诉求，抗议政府、司法腐败。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王玉波原是一名优秀教师，她在教育战线辛勤工作了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>年，在三尺讲台上教书育人数十年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年王玉波被无辜下岗，地方政府在没有任何理由的情况下，强行停止王玉波的工作，她的事业单位编制名额被掌权者卖了，档案也被篡改。并把她挂到已经破产的企业冬梅集团。下岗后校长收回了她的工资卡。没有生活来源的王玉波被逼无奈，走上了维权之路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>初东芳用铁链把自己锁在国宾馆门口的照明灯杆上，用惩罚自己的方式表达诉求。引来众多民众围观，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多名国宾馆的工作人员前来了解情况，并报</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>。消防警察开车速来救援（初东方曾于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日在天安门撒传单被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，在押回当地途中逃脱）。黑龙江省佳木斯维权访民初东方因其哥哥初少才，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日劝架，被卷入到一起刑事案件中，被判无期徒刑。而初东方为此上访告状，被治安拘留无数次，初东方说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>“哥哥案件的讯问笔录都是伪造的，鉴定结果证明哥哥初少才的讯问笔录非本人签字时，（现有字迹鉴定书证实）。本案定罪没有物证。公检法采信伪证判哥哥初少才无期徒刑。因此我对本案不服上访维权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王玉波在现场被抓后当即行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，已送往北京市海淀区拘留所执行。于丽华、吕双丽乘机离开现场。初东芳也再次被行政拘留10天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rJdK_8GxqJo/Uk90XfsktiI/AAAAAAAApBo/b_zuk9nzt78/s1600/2013-10.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rJdK_8GxqJo/Uk90XfsktiI/AAAAAAAApBo/b_zuk9nzt78/s320/2013-10.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IASGPvoMSgw/Uk90WqSggzI/AAAAAAAApBg/JeyO9HpsaNo/s1600/2013-10-04+02.42.45.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"220\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IASGPvoMSgw/Uk90WqSggzI/AAAAAAAApBg/JeyO9HpsaNo/s320/2013-10-04+02.42.45.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-N0k9SwHHUvA/Uk90ZW211MI/AAAAAAAApB4/GH90BNZCoT0/s1600/2013-10-04+03.36.18.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-N0k9SwHHUvA/Uk90ZW211MI/AAAAAAAApB4/GH90BNZCoT0/s320/2013-10-04+03.36.18.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-EoDEm6wCL6c/Uk90X8s0eXI/AAAAAAAApBw/vVpkE0LyCHs/s1600/%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F20131004155422.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"261\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-EoDEm6wCL6c/Uk90X8s0eXI/AAAAAAAApBw/vVpkE0LyCHs/s320/%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F20131004155422.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KQbrFg73aAE/Uk90aEQMq_I/AAAAAAAApCA/n4qHlRjt6c4/s1600/%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F20131004155549.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"261\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KQbrFg73aAE/Uk90aEQMq_I/AAAAAAAApCA/n4qHlRjt6c4/s320/%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F20131004155549.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址